      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>You can create simple shapes and objects at will with your nanites. Your nanites can form themselves to look like any solid object of 1 bulk or less. They can’t imitate an item’s function, moving parts, or the like. A creature that closely examines the object can determine its true nature with a successful Perception check (DC = 15 + 1-1/2 × your nanocyte level). While using this ability, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Disguise checks if an inanimate object would help your disguise.</p>"
